{"tid":2309713,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實mewe有咩好，一日有起底功能咪一樣唔安全？","createTime":"2020-12-02T17:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T19:16:29.000Z","uid":346794,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"98c79ee8048994412731933c93fe598aca233796","tid":2309713,"uid":346794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T17:24:21.000Z","msg":"其實Facebook最值錢係個algorithm,你淨係靠日期排根本出唔到你想要既野，吸引力大減<br />\n<br />\n私隱方面講真，你有曬啲post既線索，一樣咪有機會比人去起到你底，再加上你登入註冊嗰啲資料，間公司一樣可以賣你（機會幾細都好）<br />\n<br />\n其實淨係簡單計like,comment同時間整個熱門根本唔難，半年前冇野做用咗一個星期就做起過依個social media<br />\n<br />\n全匿名冇起底換一換名就唔知你邊個（利申奉公守法，警察叔叔一問我攞資料我一定合作，但係匿名登入又有得del po點搵到我就唔清楚）<br />\n<br />\n真心求教，依個social media算係我最失敗嘅作品，所以連ios我都費事上，純粹想問下點解mewe 紅到吸收下經驗出下個討論區既時候用。介面？功能？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T6Aeihm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT6Aeihm.jpg&h=c767ba25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比條link大家參考<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nngnstudio.grandom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.nngnstudio.grandom&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=2f82f9ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nngnstudio.grandom</a>"},{"pid":"f69642d48de6bf0b034d35cf88538e680514e7dc","tid":2309713,"uid":346794,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T17:26:35.000Z","msg":"好似開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f344294fc8bf907fc8f529bc3e81d55f5ff92a","tid":2309713,"uid":115579,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T17:42:51.000Z","msg":"問題在於whatsapp ig fb 全部同一間，直接賣哂你成家都仲得，仲要有實例佢干預社運 大選<br />\n最緊要一句 點解我用fb? 咪就係因為其他人仲用緊，冇㗎啦"},{"pid":"0e702d491d77ce7f01213ae3310a3249a43339e5","tid":2309713,"uid":346794,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"43f34